														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-696698">
									

<p>The things it produces often seem to be intended for use in crime or immoral acts. The part of me that loves heist movies digs the idea of an organisation dedicated to producing relics with criminal intent.</p>
<p>Basically, for me, it's about the possible target customers. The factory seems to be one of the more gloriously mercenary groups in the Foundation universe.</p>
<p>The fact that they have no known motive whatsoever is a big one as well.</p>

